parallelcc/MiCTS.body:
## Changelog
* Fix issue where "Trigger by long press gesture handle" does not work on the latest Xiaomi System Launcher (https://github.com/parallelcc/MiCTS/pull/95)
* Add Turkish translation for app and README.md (https://github.com/parallelcc/MiCTS/pull/88) @kyoyacchi
* Add Arabic translation by حبيبتي الصورة (hbybtyalswrt046) from crowdin (https://github.com/parallelcc/MiCTS/pull/112)
* Add VISTrigger app, which can trigger Gemini’s "Ask about screen" feature when Google is set as the default assistant app and Gemini is chosen in Google's Settings (https://github.com/parallelcc/MiCTS/pull/114)
* Update dependencies to the latest versions (https://github.com/parallelcc/MiCTS/pull/107 https://github.com/parallelcc/MiCTS/pull/113)

## 更新日志
* 修复最新小米桌面长按小白条触发失效的问题 (https://github.com/parallelcc/MiCTS/pull/95)
* 应用和README中新增土耳其语翻译 (https://github.com/parallelcc/MiCTS/pull/88) @kyoyacchi
* 新增阿拉伯语翻译，由 Crowdin 用户 حبيبتي الصورة （hbybtyalswrt046）提供 (https://github.com/parallelcc/MiCTS/pull/112)
* 新增VISTrigger应用，可以在设置Google为默认助理应用且Google设置里选择Gemini时，触发Gemini的"针对屏幕所示建议提问"（Ask about screen）功能 (https://github.com/parallelcc/MiCTS/pull/114)
* 更新依赖到最新版本 (https://github.com/parallelcc/MiCTS/pull/107 https://github.com/parallelcc/MiCTS/pull/113)

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/parallelcc/MiCTS/compare/v2.4...v2.5

## Changelog
* Add instructions for Samsung devices to trigger by Routines+ in README (https://github.com/parallelcc/MiCTS/pull/57) @Bananz0
* Update default device spoofing configuration to Pixel 9 Pro (https://github.com/parallelcc/MiCTS/pull/61) @lokey0905
* Add Russian language support for app and README (https://github.com/parallelcc/MiCTS/pull/67) @AlexeiCrystal
* Fix issue where "Trigger by long press home button" does not work on Xiaomi devices when "Long press the home button" is set to "None" in Button shortcuts (https://github.com/parallelcc/MiCTS/pull/68)
* Add switch for async trigger to resolve the issue where shortcut bar does not disappear as expected when default trigger delay is set  (https://github.com/parallelcc/MiCTS/pull/69 https://github.com/parallelcc/MiCTS/pull/72)
* Update dependencies to the latest versions  (https://github.com/parallelcc/MiCTS/pull/70)

## 更新日志
* README中增加三星设备通过日常程序+触发的说明 (https://github.com/parallelcc/MiCTS/pull/57) @Bananz0
* 更新机型伪装的默认配置为Pixel 9 Pro (https://github.com/parallelcc/MiCTS/pull/61) @lokey0905
* 应用和README中增加俄语 (https://github.com/parallelcc/MiCTS/pull/67) @AlexeiCrystal
* 修复小米设备上当按钮快捷方式里设置长按Home键为无时，无法通过长按Home键触发的问题 (https://github.com/parallelcc/MiCTS/pull/68)
* 增加异步触发的开关，解决通过应用快捷栏启动时，设置触发延迟无法使快捷栏消失的问题 (https://github.com/parallelcc/MiCTS/pull/69  https://github.com/parallelcc/MiCTS/pull/72)
* 更新依赖到最新版本 (https://github.com/parallelcc/MiCTS/pull/70)

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/parallelcc/MiCTS/compare/v2.3...v2.4

Add Traditional Chinese by @aes-alienrip in https://github.com/parallelcc/MiCTS/pull/39
Add Vietnamese by @nguyennhukhanh in https://github.com/parallelcc/MiCTS/pull/55
Add Japanese by @reindex-ot in https://github.com/parallelcc/MiCTS/pull/42
Add Greek by @trlef19 in https://github.com/parallelcc/MiCTS/pull/54

- 支持触发时震动（在应用设置中开启）/ Support vibration when triggering (enable in App Settings)
- 修复最新小米系统桌面上的触发问题 / Fix trigger issues on the latest Xiaomi System Launcher

系统触发服务：支持Android 15上的CSService
System trigger service: Support CSService on Android 15

支持在任意Android 9–15设备上触发，详情见 [README.md](https://github.com/parallelcc/MiCTS/blob/main/README.md)
Support triggering on any Android 9–15 device, see [README_en.md](https://github.com/parallelcc/MiCTS/blob/main/README_en.md)

增强与其他修改版launcher的兼容性
Enhanced compatibility with other modified launcher

- 支持POCO Launcher / Support POCO Launcher
- 修复1.2在公开版lsposed上hook系统桌面失败的问题 / Fix 1.2 hook system launcher failed on the public version of lsposed

修复在一些设备上无法长按小白条触发的问题
Fix the issue that the long press on the navigation handle does not trigger on some devices

支持经典导航键（三按钮）长按Home键触发
Support long press the Home button to trigger

WSTxda/MicroG-RE.body:
## MicroG RE

- Bump GMS version to `25.38.50`
- Added remove all registered apps option in cloud messaging settings
- Shrink add account FAB on scroll and add padding in preferences
- Fixed `PushNotificationAdvancedFragment` lifecycle handling
- General layout improvements
- Added russian translation
- Updated Gradle and translations
- Small changes

## GmsCore

- Auth: Migrate `SignlnConfiguration` to preprocessor-based safe parcelable
- Bump actions/setup-java from 4 to 5
- Bump actions/checkout from 4 to 5

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/WSTxda/MicroG-RE/compare/5.12...5.13

- Bump GMS version to `25.31.33` - Refresh UI with [Material 3 Expressive](https://m3.material.io/blog/building-with-m3-expressive) design - Update Login Assistant layout - Update Remove Account dialog layout - Refactored `AccountsFragment` and improved lifecycle handling - Updated signature retrieval for API compatibility - Fixed ask push notification permission dialog and data flow registration - General improvements and optimizations - Hide trust google authentication preference - Updated used libraries list - Updated MicroG RE icon resources - Prevented `LoginActivity` from being recreated on screen rotation (#76) - Enabled edge-to-edge and implement window insets listener - Added Ukrainian translation by @btncua - Updated Gradle and dependencies - Minor changes and fixes **Full Changelog**: https://github.com/WSTxda/MicroG-RE/compare/5.11...5.12
Screenshots | ![Home](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/a4da92f1-2827-42dc-9cd6-1fed8cf4ae1c) | ![Accounts](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/dbe4cc73-a4c9-427f-88af-db8233215caa) | ![Login](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/9686d591-ca9e-4ab8-8330-2fc1a38f3150) | |---|---|---| | ![Push dialog](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/62e830cb-0957-4f35-8b1d-c99d582ec9dd) | ![Push app](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/005ccf87-86e0-4852-a95d-f6ed1fcd5441) | ![Push all apps](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/b53330aa-5ceb-4aeb-a4f4-a6cb9f52d70d) |

- Bump GMS version to `25.14.62`
- Redesign login screen:
  - Added support for tablet proportion
  - Introduced material shared axis animation for opening/closing the login screen
  - Use Material3Expressive for components
- Switched to `Material3Expressive` themes and styles
- Fixed Google Photos spoof package support (#57)
- Fixed when the icon visibility is disabled, the battery optimization options are hidden in `HyperOS 2 Android 15`. also fix (#67)
- Fixed foreground service notification intent
- No disable check update button on verification
- Disable scrollbars in settings preferences
- Update included libraries list in about
- Update preference dialogs design
- Update theme colors
- Update Gradle and dependencies
- Added Turkish translation by @mikropsoft
- Added Vietnamese translation by @chemchetchagio
- Various other improvements
- Small changes

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/WSTxda/MicroG-RE/compare/5.10...5.11

## MicroG RE

- Bumped GMS version to `24.47.38`
- Added a privacy option to the settings screen
- Added an option to undo account removal via a snackbar message
- Added actions in the foreground service notification to open battery optimization and notification settings
- Added support for `x86` and `x86_64` ABIs (#45)
- Updated app icon color to align with YouTube branding changes  ![#ff0000](https://placehold.co/15x15/ff0000/ff0000.png)  →  ![#ff0033](https://placehold.co/15x15/ff0033/ff0033.png)
- Used snackbar in the UpdateChecker, improved exception handling, and rewired feature logic
- Fixed ANR exception in UpdateChecker when there is no internet connection
- Fixed usage of the deprecated `lowerCase` method
- Removed `fake-signature` (#32)
- Added missing Italian strings (#46)
- Correctly translated Cloud Messaging strings for pt-BR
- Fixed Italian translations (#44) by @0xrxL
- Made various improvements to themes, components, behavior, fonts, animations, and overall layout
- Updated Gradle and dependencies

## GmsCore

- Fixed handling of GCM topic unregistrations that return an empty token (600d0d9)
- Updated GitHub Actions workflows (5ba97df)
- Updated Gradle configuration (f2d9e44)

**Full Changelog**: [Compare 5.9...5.10](https://github.com/WSTxda/MicroG-RE/compare/5.9...5.10)

## MicroG RE

- Bump GMS version to 24.38.64
- Fixed Self-Check fragment issues and paddings
- Fixed WebView dark theme not follow system theme correctly
- Revert "Disable hide icon in launcher after click on Huawei button"
- Improve some layout things and fixes
- Changes in typography and fonts in preferences 
- Added Italian translations by @0xrxL
- Added Indonesian (Bahasa) translations by @okkidwi
- Small strings translations changes
- Enable gradle build cache

## GmsCore

- Account settings: Allow profile picture page (microg#2535)
- Account Settings: Take product name into MyActivity page (microg#2491)
- SafeParcelProcessor: Fix code generator (microg#2525)
- Push: Fix ask push permission dialog
- SafeParcel: Mark processor as incremental
- Improve log of service request
- Bump gradle/actions from 3 to 4

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/WSTxda/MicroG-RE/compare/5.8...5.9

- Fix hide icon in launcher icon option and change activity to app settings in system app info

### 5.7

- Bump GMS version to 24.31.36
- Add spoof package support for Google News and Google Photos
- Improvement hide icon in launcher option
- Improvement design of accounts and login screen and support landscape mode
- Set hide icon switch state match component state
- Hide "logged in" category if have none account in list
- Adjust some text styles in preference layout
- Added RTL support for layout
- Added polish translation by @Patriot99
- Added arabic translation by @muhammadbahaa2001

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/WSTxda/MicroG-RE/compare/5.6...5.8

**Hotfix: fixed ActivityNotFoundExeption for accounts settings link due package spoofing in RVX, REX**
- Bump GMS version to 24.26.62

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/WSTxda/MicroG-RE/compare/5.4...5.6

- Bump GMS Version to 24.26.32
- Improve the signOut method of AuthSignlnService
- Added options for manage YouTube data and history for activity handler
- Tap in "Google account" or "Manage your Google Account" in YouTube/YT Music. open "Accounts" in MicroG Settings
- Move privacy screen to preference options
- Update gradle and dependencies


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/WSTxda/MicroG-RE/compare/5.4...5.5

## MicroG RE

- Bump GMS version to 24.21.55
- Update gradle dependencies
- Change default group id to ReVanced
- Refactor accounts manager screen
- Login: Switch to m3 proguess indicator
- Fix: Handler YouTube Music account manager link
- Make update list in main thread to prevent crash

## GmsCore

- Update Gradle Wrapper validation action
- Add update check for Github actions (microg#2342)
- Auth: Remove unnecessary prompts
- Auth: update credentials feature version
- Auth: Correctly handle permission for requests with token request options (microg#2322)
- Add google.sent_time extra to C2DM receive intent
- Only include sent time when valid, also add TTL
- Push: Do not allow app data to override service fields

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/WSTxda/MicroG-RE/compare/5.3...5.4

- Change package ID to ReVanced to support new GmsCore patcher
- Enable necessary settings by default

This versions not included playback and buffer fixes, need spoof player patcher to works

New version with this fix available soon :)

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/WSTxda/MicroG-RE/compare/5.2...5.3
